I recommend using /substitute instead of gagging and /echoing.  This way,
other triggers and hilites of lower priority (less than 999 in this example)
can still apply to the reformatted line.

  /def -F -p999 -mglob -t'\[INFO\]: *' infochannel = \
      /substitute [INFO]: $[ftime("%y/%m/%d %H:%M",time())] %{-1}

See /help topics:  /substitute, time(), ftime(), $[], priority


