You must have sub=full.  I recommend leaving sub=off, because most of the
time you probably don't want %, $, etc. to be interpreted.  In those cases
when you _do_ want evaluation, stick /eval at the beginning of the line,
or define a keybinding like the one below to let you evaluate a line by
hitting ESC RETURN.

