The %{emulation} variable determines whether ANSI attribute codes received
from a server are stripped or converted to TF's intneral form.  Attributes
generated from within TF (/echo -a, triggers, %status_fields, etc.) are
always in TF's internal form, and %{emulation} has no effect on them.

