In newer versions of tf, use this:

; Syntax: /ql file line_number
;
; Puts line line_number from file into the input buffer
;
/def -i ql = \
  /let _handle=$[tfopen({1}, "r")]%;\
  /let _line_number=%2%;\
  /let _line=%;\
  /while (tfread(_handle, _line) != -1 & --_line_number) /done%;\
  /input %_line%;\
  /test kbgoto(0)

If you specify a line that is outside the range of lines in the file, the
last line will be used.



