and it interrupts the entire macro, not just the read.  So, when using
tfread(), you need to either provide another way to break the loop
(e.g., typing "/endpaste" during /paste), or just don't use it with
input from the keyboard.  /writefile is intended to be used with 
tfin from a pipe; e.g.,

  /eval /list <options> %| /writefile [-a] <file>

is nearly identical to

  /save [-a] <file> <options>

